<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the method Zend_Search_Lucene::close(), the following line should be added:</p>

<p>$this-&gt;_closed = true;</p>

<p>This will ensure that a close() will not be called by the destructor if previously called manually.</p>

<p>Another good idea would be to check the $_closed flag at the beginning of closed() and throw an exception if it is true.</p>

